OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783855166
OL,3,CTwo men charged after police find more
OL,4,Cthan 1,000 cannabis plants
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged after police
OL,7,Ffound a large cannabis factory
OL,8,Fcontaining more than 1,000 plants near
OL,9,FBasingstoke.
OL,11,FOfficers attended a property on
OL,12,FCompton Way, Sherfield Park, at around
OL,13,F9 am on Thursday 9 July and discovered
OL,14,Faround 200 plants in each of the six
OL,15,Fgrow rooms.
OL,17,FQuoc Toan Nguyen, 45, of no fixed
OL,18,Fabode, and Thao Quang Ha, 53, of no
OL,19,Ffixed abode, have been charged with
OL,20,Fbeing concerned in the production of a
OL,21,Fcontrolled drug of Class B.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
