OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783855166
OL,3,CTwo men charged after police find more
OL,4,Cthan 1,000 cannabis plants
OL,6,FGosport Police said: "Large-scale
OL,7,Foperations are often run by organised
OL,8,Fcrime gangs, who are likely to engage
OL,9,Fin very serious violence involving
OL,10,Fweapons, such as firearms.
OL,12,F"The electrical requirement to grow a
OL,13,Flarge number of plants is also
OL,14,Fdangerous and can be a huge fire risk,
OL,15,Fputting neighbouring properties, and
OL,16,Flives, in danger.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
