OL,3,CTwo men charged after police find more
OL,4,Cthan 1,000 cannabis plants
OL,6,F"We encourage people to please
OL,7,Fcontinue to report suspicious
OL,8,Fbehaviour and suspected drug dealing
OL,9,Fin your neighbourhood to police, as
OL,10,Fthe information you provide helps us
OL,11,Fdevelop the bigger picture that leads
OL,12,Fus to take action."
OL,14,FPolice are asking anyone with
OL,15,Finformation to get in touch, quoting
OL,16,F44260326170.
